{"tid":1787615,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問會否索償 稱「黑警嚟喎」","createTime":"2019-12-18T05:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T05:09:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74552c3041c3c3201c05081bd178d57739603b16","tid":1787615,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:02:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191218/W4UFUOJ6AEERGSMW6JUS3JSIPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191218%2FW4UFUOJ6AEERGSMW6JUS3JSIPQ%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BusvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=e6139e6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191218%2FW4UFUOJ6AEERGSMW6JUS3JSIPQ%2F&h=b5f725b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191218/W4UFUOJ6AEERGSMW6JUS3JSIPQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n被問會否索償 稱「黑警嚟喎」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191218/large/1576601362_9b17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191218%2Flarge%2F1576601362_9b17.jpg&h=d347cec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉案商人（左）昨獲撤控後離開法院。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】商人遭警毆打，卻被控襲警，最終雖獲撤控，但事件已令他身心受創，生活大受影響。被問到會否循民事途徑向警方追討賠償，商人指「嗰啲黑警嚟㗎喎」，他身旁的女親友則指要先與律師商討，不排除向警方索償。有大狀指出，被告確可向警方提出民事索償，但需要提供足夠證據以證明傷勢或損失，否則審訊時只能「靠口講，睇吓個官信邊個」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：社區放TG 「如攻擊市民」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可申請披露警員姓名<br />\n<br />\n大律師潘展平指出，被告可以向警方提出民事追討， 例如提出人身傷亡索償案件，就疼痛、痛苦與喪失生活樂趣、收入損失等索償。但被告需要提供足夠證據，例如閉路電視片段及證人等，以證明當時遭警員無理襲擊，當中現場片段是關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n惟潘坦言，若被告傷勢輕微，即使勝訴亦只會獲得微薄賠償金，至於名譽損失，除了證明警方犯錯外，還要證明該錯誤損害被告名譽。<br />\n<br />\n潘又指，被告有權向法庭申請披露涉案匿名警員的姓名，但「畀唔畀係另一回事」，因為此類案件大多是控告警務處長，而非直接控告涉案警員本人。不過，被告可嘗試以需要傳召涉案警員作供為由，要求法庭披露相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉偉琪、楊家樂"},{"pid":"388e82c1201c67c834c3ef68662542ae3cf88250","tid":1787615,"uid":1891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n毋忘元朗恐襲事件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDdw0Ke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDdw0Ke.jpg&h=23920099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RRKyxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RRKyxN.jpg&h=fcfe2918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wrd5kKm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrd5kKm.jpg&h=81977b54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSrB86f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSrB86f.jpg&h=51458dba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9103c9d9d170ecb63b5acce9d0aa4f10df0dc81","tid":1787615,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suoQ2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suoQ2O.jpg&h=203fa15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"640718ff5bede849e10e898f84a7c5f1a3615b63","tid":1787615,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"心水清"},{"pid":"95e9ab3d29226c0f0706446d50a9b9f3788fad4b","tid":1787615,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b42aa3475fcf1644029ccbfebfe00b95fa579e7","tid":1787615,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">否則審訊時只能「靠口講，睇吓個官信邊個」</span><br />\n<br />\n官: 黑警係公務員 可靠證人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca3b094b52456de56aa7edab89a8bc7cb95b932","tid":1787615,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}